          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Your own private labeled, EPA Safer Choice Approved product<br/>is an exceptional add-on sale on every job and a perfect way to leave your “Unforgettable Brand” behind to your customers! Like most service companies, you want your own private label that contains your company logo and call back information. The problem always has been the high minimum bottle purchase and the cost of your own professionally printed labels.</p><p><strong>Environmental Biotech now offers, a low cost and low<br/>minimum case purchase!</strong></p><p>How important is keeping YOUR company name in your current customer’s home? How much do you currently spend marketing to current and past customers, so that emergency phone call goes to you and not your competitor? Keeping your name and brand in your customer’s home maximizes the chance of the customer calling you when that toilet plugs, or the faucet leaks. Traditional branding items such as pens, magnets, and stickers always end up in the trash<br/>of junk drawer.</p>",
